race.description: Nova Trotters Cup Discretionary Handicap Pace (G2)
race.comment: MAJESTIC GA GA (14) is flying having landed a winning hat trick when leading to cruise home by more than 10m at Pinjarra on Monday. Came from the outside barrier to win a G3 here two back. Proven at this longer distance and is going well enough to overcome the 50m handicap. Manners let GRUMPEE (7) down when favourite in the Trotters Sprint last start but he had impressively won his previous two outings, one in a standing start race. Can win if he gets it right. MY LIGHTNING MCQUEEN NZ (9) was runner-up to MAJESTIC GA GA at G3 level last start, giving her two wins and two seconds form her last four starts. Go well again. PATCHED (12) drew on the back row and worked when racing wide last start but boxed on. Each way hope.
